reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My tween niece wanted makeup for her birthday. This was such a great value and cute set. Teal is her favorite color. The makeup is perfect for her. She doesn't need $100 palettes at this age. She's happy I'm the coolest aunt. Highly recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Ok quality makeup and brushes
reviews.reviewText: Its a nice makeup box, comes with the 4 trays of makeup. The quality isn't too bad either, the eyeshadow trays include nudes, browns, yellows, tans and more on one side and greens, grays, lavenders, purples and dark pinks. Very nice they and they all go on smoothly and stay vibrant. Doesn't feel caked on either. There's also a tray with glittery cream like eye shadows, and then a row of concealers in every color. The last tray has contours colors and blush colors. Also has 4 small lip colors one gloss which aren't the best for long wear they start to clump up after awhile, has black liner, colored lip liner 3 brushes for eyeshadows and one dark brown eyebrow color and one clear chapstick. I love the box so cute and great for traveling. It's worth the cost for sure.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect Gift for the Budding Make-up Artist
reviews.reviewText: FIRST: I was blown away at how well this kit was packaged! Special attention was given to ensure the powders and shadows were protected from breakage during shipping. VERY well packaged. Great job!SECOND: The aesthetics are fabulous! It is a beautiful, hard bodied, metallic purple case. Perfect for travel or just storing neatly at home. The case is very well made and organizes the make-up and supplies in a way that makes sense. Super for those that travel for various types of competitions.THIRD: A nice selection of colors in shadows, blushes, lipsticks, glosses. A great starter set for practicing make-up techniques. Great for pageants, competitions, theater. Everything you need, whether on-the-go or hanging out at home. A very nice gift for pre-teen or teen!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I will admit that this set was cheaper when I ordered it then what it is now, but it is of much higher quality than what I would typically consider for a teenager. It has a ton of stuff included and is truly an all in one kit to get you started. If you consider how much a single mascara or eye liner costs at a grocery store, it justifies the price tag much better.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wonderful gift for teen
reviews.reviewText: Love how cute the kit is and would highly recommend it as a gift for a girl just starting out with makeup. The variety of colors on the eye palates is nice and I like how the kit is organized. I got it for myself and my two girls are too young for it yet but when they are older I hope to purchase something just like this for them

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love being a girl
reviews.reviewText: This is the second Cosmetic Train Case I’ve ordered. It’s also the second time I found myself surprised by the beautiful selection of wearable, usable cosmetics inside. I’ll be honest, I really love the train cases and know that even if I don’t use much inside, I’ll use that case for ages. I collect many things and train cases are a beautiful way to store them. HOWEVER, the cosmetics are beautiful, 48 wearable eyeshadows! I’m quite sure I’ll wear all but maybe 6 of them. I think these cases are a hidden treasure that many women don’t find or assume they could use. They appear to be marketed towards girls and teens and they are great gifts for them… but women can enjoy them too. Mine is going on a girls trip and we’re gonna have fun with it. I definitely recommend it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars I really wanted to like this
reviews.reviewText: Let me start by saying, that I have yet to try everything in this makeup set. I am a big fan of the gel eyeliner and brushes. When it comes to the eyeshadow pallets. There is a nice range of colors that go on and blend nicely. The plastic they're held in is very flimsy. They ripped when I tried to take the tape off to open them. The case is super cute and I love the color. However, the latch is not to be trusted.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy train case makeup ain't hightm end (but expected)
reviews.reviewText: This was a fun little train case. I have gotten many of these over the years and the makeup is pretty comparable. It isn't high end so be sure not to expect that. The makeup is fun for a tween or teen girl as i would expect they would be very excited to get this. The train case itself is sturdy and this is a great start to a makeup collection for someone new to 💄 makeup.
